Creating a basic ansible playbook to automate system using SSH:
$ vim ~/playbook.yaml

- name: ping 
  hosts:server
  tasks: 
          -name: ping
           ansible.builtIn.ping :
          -name: debug
           ansible.builtIn.debug :
                     msg: Hello world 


RUN YOUR PLAYBOOK USING :
$ ansible-playbook ~/playbook.yaml
